# game/Scenes/Mari/MariDates/mariparkdate.rpy:29
translate chinese mariparkstartdate_1911c1ec:

    # "We walk and chit-chat, stopping to let the dogs sniff everything."
    "我们边走边闲聊，时不时停下来让狗狗们到处嗅嗅。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariDates/mariparkdate.rpy:31
translate chinese mariparkstartdate_7f2e9838:

    # "We walk and chit-chat for a while."
    "我们边走边聊了一会儿。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariDates/mariparkdate.rpy:36
translate chinese mariparkstartdate_da6e9f35:

    # "Appa and Momo find a particularly good spot to sniff and neither wants to move for a while, so Mari and I use the opportunity to talk."
    "阿帕和莫莫找到一个特别适合嗅闻的地方，两只都不愿动弹，于是玛丽和我趁机聊了起来。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariDates/mariparkdate.rpy:43
translate chinese mariparkstartdate_fbe66623:

    # "When we reach the bench, the dogs wander around, playing, while Mari and I chat."
    "走到长椅旁时，狗狗们四处游荡玩耍，玛丽和我则继续聊天。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariDates/mariparkdate.rpy:45
translate chinese mariparkstartdate_400bdaa9:

    # "Eventually, we reach the bench that we sat at before."
    "最终，我们来到之前坐过的长椅旁。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariDates/mariparkdate.rpy:52
translate chinese mariparkstartdate_47364019:

    # "Damn, she's gorgeous."
    "天啊，她真美。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariDates/mariparkdate.rpy:56
translate chinese mariparkstartdate_d7d7fcbe:

    # "The dogs play around the park bench, getting pets from people walking past as Mari and I sit on the bench and talk."
    "狗狗们在公园长椅周围嬉戏，路过的行人会摸摸它们，而玛丽和我则坐在长椅上交谈。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariDates/mariparkdate.rpy:57
translate chinese mariparkstartdate_2531bb8c:

    # "It's not as calm as it would be without them here, but watching the dogs play is fun too."
    "虽然没有它们在场时那么宁静，但看着狗狗们玩耍也挺有意思的。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariDates/mariparkdate.rpy:59
translate chinese mariparkstartdate_82bac2ae:

    # "We sit next to each other on the bench for a bit, listening to the breeze blow through the leaves."
    "我们并排坐在长椅上片刻，聆听微风拂过树叶的声响。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariDates/mariparkdate.rpy:62
translate chinese mariparkstartdate_6cb3d585:

    # "I put my arm around her and hold her close."
    "我搂住她的肩膀，将她紧紧拥入怀中。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariDates/mariparkdate.rpy:66
translate chinese mariparkstartdate_df5a3267:

    # "Then we make out a bit, kissing passionately for some time."
    "接着我们亲热了一会儿，热情地接吻了好一阵子。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariDates/mariparkdate.rpy:70
translate chinese mariparkstartdate_2c1c5eb4:

    # "Then we start walking back towards the car. The dogs both seem tired and ready to take a nap after the big day."
    "然后我们开始往车子那边走。经历了这么忙碌的一天，两只狗看起来都累坏了，似乎随时都要睡个觉。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariDates/mariparkdate.rpy:72
translate chinese mariparkstartdate_5be0eff7:

    # "Then it is time to go back to the car and take her home."
    "是时候回到车里，送她回家了。"

